import React from 'react'; import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; import { Search, Bell, Calendar, MapPin, Clock, ArrowRight } from 'lucide-react'; const Dashboard = ({ user, events, theme, regCount, unreadCount }) => { const navigate = useNavigate(); const isDark = theme === 'dark'; const styles = { // REDUCED PADDING TO 10PX container: { padding: '10px 20px', backgroundColor: isDark ? '#0f172a' : '#f8fafc', minHeight: '100vh', }, header: { display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center', marginBottom: '20px', flexWrap: 'wrap', gap: '10px' }, profileSection: { display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: '10px', cursor: 'pointer' }, avatar: { width: '40px', height: '40px', borderRadius: '50%', objectFit: 'cover', border: '2px solid #6366f1' }, name: { fontSize: '16px', fontWeight: '800', color: isDark ? '#fff' : '#1e293b' }, rightHeader: { display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: '10px' }, searchContainer: { display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', backgroundColor: '#fff', borderRadius: '50px', padding: '8px 15px', width: '280px', border: '1px solid #e2e8f0' }, input: { border: 'none', outline: 'none', fontSize: '13px', flex: 1 }, notifBtn: { width: '40px', height: '40px', borderRadius: '50%', backgroundColor: '#fff', border: '1px solid #e2e8f0', display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center', cursor: 'pointer', color: '#6366f1' }, heroBanner: { display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center', backgroundColor: '#e0e7ff', borderRadius: '16px', padding: '30px', marginBottom: '30px' }, heroTitle: { fontSize: '24px', fontWeight: '800', marginBottom: '10px', color: '#1e1b4b' }, heroBtn: { backgroundColor: '#1e1b4b', color: '#fff', border: 'none', padding: '10px 20px', borderRadius: '8px', cursor: 'pointer' }, statsRow: { display: 'flex', gap: '15px', marginBottom: '30px' }, statCard: { flex: 1, backgroundColor: '#fff', padding: '20px', borderRadius: '12px', border: '1px solid #e2e8f0', display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: '15px' }, sectionHeader: { display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center', marginBottom: '15px' }, grid: { display: 'grid', gridTemplateColumns: 'repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr))', gap: '20px' }, eventCard: { backgroundColor: '#fff', borderRadius: '12px', overflow: 'hidden', border: '1px solid #e2e8f0', cursor: 'pointer', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column' }, cardImage: { width: '100%', height: '150px', objectFit: 'cover' }, cardBody: { padding: '15px' } }; return (
{/* Header */}
navigate('/profile')}>
Welcome back,
{user.name.split(' ')[0]}
{/* Hero */}

Discover New Skills!

{/* Stats */}
{events.length}
Events
{regCount}
Registered
{/* Grid */}

Upcoming Events

navigate('/events')}>View all
{events.slice(0, 3).map(event => (
navigate(`/event-details/${event.id}`)}>
{event.title}
{event.date}
))}
); }; export default Dashboard;
